11 FLOOR SUBSTITUTE
12 A Joint Resolution directing the Secretary of State
to refer to the people for their approval or
13 rejection a proposed amendment to Section 2 of
Article XXV-A of the Oklahoma Constitution;
14 clarifying certain Medicaid coverage requirement;
removing prohibition on imposing certain eligibility
15 restrictions; directing the Secretary of State to
refer to the people for their approval or rejection a
16 proposed amendment to repeal Sections 1, 2, 3, and 4
of Article XXV-A of the Oklahoma Constitution, which
17 relate to Medicaid expansion; making repealers
contingent upon certain federal action; ordering a
18 legislative referendum; defining terms; requiring
state to provide certain medical assistance;
19 requiring Oklahoma Health Care Authority to maximize
certain federal funding; making provisions contingent
20 upon certain federal action; providing ballot title;
providing for codification; and directing filing.
21
22
23
